PI® Web API

PI® API & Dev Tools

API Documentation

Introduction

Project Insight provides a simple-to-use REST API\, so you may build your own tools to retrieve and manage your data within your applications and environment. This easy to use guide is intended for developers. It includes information about using the API as well as how to access the API methods with coding samples.

Our core API will continue to undergo development to provide you with more functions to help you tool your needs. We"ll keep you up-to-date with any late breaking changes and modifications\, so you can be well informed and maintain your existing applications with the latest updates.

You can also search our Knowledgebase for tutorials\, release notes and other information about how Project Insight provides support for REST API.

  • Project Managers may find using the Microsoft Power Query tool to be the biggest thing since sliced bread!
